If not too much effort, would it be possible to add support for str.itoa() functionality?

This snippet below is failing for Icarus but passing for Xcelium / VCS.

```
module testbench;
  string str;
  int val;
  initial begin
    val = 5;
    str.itoa(val);
    $display("STR is %s", str);
  end
endmodule
```

